# Game Idea :



The game consists of 16 cards arranged randomly in a grid. each with different image on one side.

1. The player flips one card over to reveal its image.

2. The player then turns over a second card, trying to find the corresponding card with the same image.

3. If the cards match, you start your way to win it and start to flip

Other cards.

4. If the cards do not match, both cards are returned to their hidden state.

5. The game ends once all cards have been correctly matched.

6. Scoring board with player results appears (time /number of stars).
